`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIIT Nagpur operates in Nagpur, Maharashtra, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning AI/ML and data, Computer vision, Embedded systems and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across top public tech institutes, anchor your choices with labs, facilities, and sponsored work rather than brand alone."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Because the institute is embedded in Nagpur, interns can tap into nearby industry partners, field sites, and alumni-led startups. This often translates to problem statements with real datasets or hardware constraints rather than purely academic exercises."}),`
